    <div id="help-main">
        <div id="help-board" class="box-blur">
            <p>Click <span class="text-italic">"LOCATE"</span> auto generate
                <span class="text-italic">LATITUDE and LONGTITUDE</span>
                <br>
                (allow website to use your location)
            </p>

            <button class="button-common">LOCATE</button>

            <p>or fill in the
                <span class="text-italic">LATITUDE and LONGTITUDE</span>
