            </p>

            <div id="help-sub-board" class="box-blur">
                <form style="
                            display: flex; 
                            flex-direction: column; 
                            align-items: center; 
                            gap: 10px;">
                    <label for="">LATITUDE</label>
                    <input class="input-common" type="text">
